sentences.sentence: Wendy, I do believe that's your little whelp!
sentences.translation: 温迪，我相信那只是你的小狼崽！

sentences.sentence: This whelp is the only person she loves!
sentences.translation: 这狗崽子便是她唯一钟爱的人了！

sentences.sentence: I had no idea what to do with this whelp.
sentences.translation: 我完全不知道该把这个崽子怎么办。
